site_name: Kingswell House and land to the rear of 453
description: Demolition of existing building and mixed use redevelopment of part 2, 3 , 4 and 5 storey buildings to provide 123 residential units (comprising 34 x 1 bed, 65 x 2 bed and 24 x 3 bed) together with 448 m2 of retail (Class A1), public and private amenity open space, childrens play area, provision of surface and under croft parking for 85 spaces with through vehicular access from Kingsway to Emilia Close.
